      <title>加州发生火灾 1000 人被迫撤离</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-18/post-fire-in-california-forces-1-000-to-evacuate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洛杉矶北部野火肆虐，浓烟滚滚，向南蔓延，迫使 1,000 多人撤离 — — 随着干燥的风吹过山丘，火势势头愈演愈烈。火灾已烧毁超过 14,000 英亩土地。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-18/post-fire-in-california-forces-1-000-to-evacuate</guid>
